446
00:34:30,413 --> 00:34:33,893
# Kidnap the Sandy Claws #
# Throw him in a box #

447
00:34:33,997 --> 00:34:37,412
# Bury him for 90 years #
# Then see if he talks #

448
00:34:38,957 --> 00:34:42,056
# Then Mr. Oogie Boogie Man #

449
00:34:42,158 --> 00:34:44,459
# Can take the whole thing #
# over then #

450
00:34:45,677 --> 00:34:48,939
# He'll be so pleased #
# I do declare #

451
00:34:49,037 --> 00:34:51,655
# That he will cook him rare #
# Whee #

452
00:34:57,773 --> 00:35:00,937
# I say that we take a cannon #
