456
00:35:11,117 --> 00:35:14,794
# Kidnap the Sandy Claws #
# Tie him in a bag #

457
00:35:14,893 --> 00:35:17,260
# Throw him in the ocean #
# Then see if he is sad #

458
00:35:17,357 --> 00:35:20,935
# Because Mr. Oogie Boogie #
