459
00:35:21,037 --> 00:35:26,056
# If I were on his boogie list #
# I'd get out of town #

460
00:35:27,437 --> 00:35:30,503
# He'll be so pleased #
# by our success #

461
00:35:30,605 --> 00:35:33,256
# That he'll reward us too #
# I'll bet #

462
00:35:34,477 --> 00:35:37,347
# Perhaps he'll make #
# his special brew #

463
